OL,3,CFormer Scotland rugby captain Stuart
OL,4,CHogg admits domestic abuse
OL,6,FFormer Scotland rugby international
OL,7,FStuart Hogg has admitted abusing his
OL,8,Festranged wife over the course of five
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,FHogg, 32, from Hawick, had been due to
OL,12,Fstand trial at Selkirk Sheriff Court
OL,13,Fon Monday but pleaded guilty to a
OL,14,Fsingle charge when he appeared at the
OL,15,Fcourt.
OL,17,FThe father-of-four arrived at Selkirk
OL,18,FSheriff Court accompanied by his
OL,19,Fparents and admitted a single charge
OL,20,Fof domestic abuse against his
OL,21,Festranged wife, between 2019 and 2024.
